For the system with the ratio of the initial reagents PbI2:CH3NH3I = 1:1, it was found that the single-phase product is formed at 70–80 °С by the reaction:1PbIz+CH3NH3I→70−80°СCH3NH3PbI3.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
